\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line Tshwane College of Commerce and Computer Studies is not yet registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training as a private higher education provider and is not yet accredited to offer higher education programmes by the HEQC. The institution has also applied for a Diploma in Travel and Tourism Management\'2C a Bachelor of Business Administration\'2C a Diploma in Financial Accounting and a Diploma in Information Technology. \cell \pard 

